data.description: Reduced price!!  Welcome to Potomac Station, this move-in-ready townhouse has 3 bedrooms and 2 and 1/2 baths.  42" cabinets in the kitchen with an island for extra seating and storage, dining room, and living room along with a deck on the level.  3rd level has the primary bedroom and bathroom, along with 2 other bedrooms and bathroom.  Nice to have 3rd level laundry room as well.  The basement has a large that can be a possible 4th bedroom, rec room or office.  Schedule your tour now.
